snippets.title: CloudDeploy cancelAutomationRun Sample
snippets.description: Cancels an AutomationRun. The `state` of the `AutomationRun` after cancelling is `CANCELLED`. `CancelAutomationRun` can be called on AutomationRun in the state `IN_PROGRESS` and `PENDING`; AutomationRun in a different state returns an `FAILED_PRECONDITION` error.
